      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a meticulously maintained VANOS system and has undergone proactive rod bearing replacement with documented service history. The chassis is structurally sound with verified subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension retains factory-spec geometry with zero bushing deflection. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior remains in concours-level condition with original factory paint depth. A collector-grade specimen with a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline that remains as sharp as the day it left Regensburg.",
