      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, retaining its deep factory luster with no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections of any kind. Every body panel is original with perfect alignment. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats are supple and show no signs of creasing or wear, the carpets are spotless, and the dashboard remains pristine. All electronic components, switches, and displays function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition, delivering a smooth, powerful, and quiet ride. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, showing no leaks or grime. I possess a comprehensive service history binder documenting every maintenance interval performed by certified technicians. I welcome and encourage a third-party pre-purchase inspection at a shop of your choice to confirm this vehicle's extraordinary state. This is a rare chance to own a museum-quality example for your collection.",
